description: Overlay Zoning. The dataset contains polygons representing overlay zoning districts, as submitted to the DC Office of Zoning, created for the District of Columbia Office of Zoning (DCOZ). Overlay zoning districts were identified from official adopted zoning and unofficial zoning documents and heads-up digitized from the 1995/1999 orthophotographs. For the most up-to-date information, contact the DCOZ directly.
